      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "@VCD &quot;it seems that has, can, should prefixes are not part of the specification&quot; - Hence, that&#39;s the whole problem with blindly trying to follow these types of specifications. They usually just cover basic scenarios. The main thing is, use intuitive variable and method names that make sense and that people maintaining this code later will understand. Common sense goes a long way here."
