      "comment_id" : 139821827,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "That doesn&#39;t really make sense to me. If I&#39;m forced to chose between <code>setActive</code> and <code>unsetActive</code> I would have to do something like <code>if (blue || red) { setActive(); } else { unsetActive(); }</code> instead of just <code>setActive(blue || red)</code>."
